        <div class="generaor-name-search-result">
            <div class="generator-results-header">
                <h3 class="generator-results-header-title">Names for your cat</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="generator-results">
                <p class="generator-name" id="result">Artsiomati</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="calc-info">
        <h3 class="calc-info-title-name">There are several reasons why need use a cat name generator:</h3>
        <p class="calc-info-text">

            Inspiration: A cat name generator can provide inspiration for unique and creative names that you may not have thought of on your own.

            Convenience: A cat name generator can be a convenient way to quickly generate a list of potential names for your new feline friend, saving you time and effort.

            Variety: A cat name generator can provide a wide variety of names, including traditional, modern, and unique options. This can help you to find the perfect name that suits your cat's personality and appearance.

            Personalization: cat name generators allow you to input specific characteristics or information about your cat, such as its color or breed, to generate personalized name suggestions.

